zh_CN.DialogText: 哈哈，肯定不是带着放射的阴风。

en_US.DialogText: Ha ha, definitely not with the radiation of the Bleak wind.
OK, what are you looking for me for?

zh_CN.DialogText: 你开始帮助别人了，这是好事，我看到了你能给我们带来...旧时代的技术。

en_US.DialogText: You're starting to help others. It's a good thing. I see you can bring us Old age technology.

zh_CN.DialogText: 那么你给我们带来的就事远古时期的技术了，比如木工....抱歉。

en_US.DialogText: So what you brought us is the technology of ancient times, such as carpentry ... I 'm sorry.

zh_CN.DialogText: 所以你也是来找我帮什么忙的咯？

en_US.DialogText: So why are you here to help me?

zh_CN.DialogText: 我是想来找你谈谈交易，作为公社主席

en_US.DialogText: I wanted to talk to you about the deal.As chairman of the commune

zh_CN.DialogText: 我也听说你最近一直在收集各种吃的还有喝的还有一些小零件。

en_US.DialogText: I also heard that you have been collecting all kinds of food and drink and some small parts recently.

zh_CN.DialogText: 我老了，很多工作不能完成...所以我希望你能来帮我，我会给你这些稀缺的零件，反正我也不会用。

en_US.DialogText: I'm old and can't finish a lot of work So I hope you can help me. I'll give you these scarce parts. I won't use them anyway.
